7.2 Return on Investment

For 1000 MWe Plant ($5B capital cost):

Revenue Benefits:

· Increased Capacity Factor: 7% improvement = $35M/year
· Reduced Forced Outages: $10M/year
· Extended Plant Life: 20-year extension = $500M NPV

Cost Savings:

· Reduced Maintenance: 28% reduction = $5M/year
· Reduced Staffing: 15% reduction = $3M/year
· Fuel Efficiency: 2% improvement = $4M/year

Total Annual Benefit: $57M/year

Payback Period:

```
Payback = Initial Investment / Annual Benefit
        = $11M / $57M = 0.19 years (2.3 months)
```

Net Present Value (20 years, 5% discount rate):

```
NPV = Σ (Annual Benefit / (1 + r)^t) - Initial Investment
    = $712M - $11M = $701M
```

